org.hibernate.sql

Interface JdbcValueExtractor<J>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractJdbcValueExtractor, EmptyJdbcValueExtractor, ResolvingSqlSelectionImpl

    public interface JdbcValueExtractor<J>
    The low-level contract for extracting (reading) values to JDBC.
    See Also:
    JdbcValueBinder, SqlExpressableType
    "API Note:"
    At the JDBC-level we always deal with simple/basic values; never composites, entities, collections, etc
